> **Control how closely the AI follows your comment templates**  

## ğŸ“‹ Overview  
Template Adherence lets you balance **creativity vs. structure** when generating comments. Adjust it in **AI Tools â†’ Template Adherence Control** using the **real-time slider** (0.0 â€“ 1.0).  

---

## âš™ï¸ Configuration  

| Slider Position | Behavior | Use Case |
|----------------|----------|----------|
| **0.0 - 0.3** | Very Creative | Loose inspiration, highly natural |
| **0.4 - 0.6** | Balanced | Mix of structure + creativity |
| **0.7 - 0.9** | Template-Focused | Closely follows template |
| **1.0** | Strict Template | Exact structure, no changes |

ğŸ”’ **Important:** Content wrapped in `*asterisks*` (CTAs, links) is **always preserved**, regardless of adherence.  

