## ğŸ¨ Examples  

**Template:**  
```
"Great video! *Subscribe to my channel* for more content. *Check out my website* for resources."
```  

**Video:** *How to Trade Bitcoin in 2025*  

| Adherence | AI Output | Behavior |
|-----------|-----------|----------|
| **0.2 (Creative)** | "Wow, this Bitcoin guide is exactly what I needed! *Subscribe to my channel* for more crypto insights. *Check out my website* for advanced strategies." | Conversational, adds context |
| **0.5 (Balanced)** | "Great video on Bitcoin trading! Really helpful insights for 2025. *Subscribe to my channel* for more crypto content. *Check out my website* for additional resources." | Balanced, relevant |
| **0.8 (Template-Focused)** | "Great video! *Subscribe to my channel* for more content. *Check out my website* for some other resources." | Mostly template, minor edits |
| **1.0 (Strict)** | "Great video! *Subscribe to my channel* for more content. *Check out my website* for resources." | Exact template |

